* Task 2 fixture: CALLNAT static extraction
* Contains two literal CALLNAT calls plus surrounding non-call statements
* to prove zero false edges are produced for non-call lines.

DEFINE DATA
LOCAL
  1 STATUS-CODE (N2)
END DEFINE

CALLNAT 'A'

WRITE 'Processing'

CALLNAT 'B'

MOVE 42 TO STATUS-CODE

END
